``To call room service, please to open door and call ROOM
SERVICE.''
Did you guess it? Travel Trivia answer: <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Phoenix</ENAMEX> is <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">America</ENAMEX>'s
